# CTF Palette Lab — example environment file
# Copy to .env.local for local overrides. Real .env* files are gitignored.

# Vite base path. Leave unset (default "/") for local dev or for a user/org
# GitHub Pages site / custom domain. For a project site set this to the
# repository name surrounded by slashes, e.g. /CTF-Palette-Lab/.
# In CI the GitHub Actions workflow sets this automatically from the repo name.
# VITE_BASE_PATH=/
